<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Coventry Hills</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The community was established in 1991 and is bound by the Deerfoot Trail on the east, the Stoney Trail to the north, the Harvest Hills Boulevard on the west and the Country Hills Boulevard on the south.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Home to the north of 15,000 residents, the Coventry Hills real estate offers a variety of housing options that majorly comprise of detached and semi-detached homes built in the 90s and the 2000s. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">With an average price of just over $400,000, nearly 95% of the dwellings in the area are privately owned and only 5% available for renting.</p>
        </div>
